user.biography: Healing through positive words, art and light. To buy click the link below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 09, 2021. May be an image of outdoors, tree and text that says 'Negative people need drama like they need oxygen. Stay positive and take their breath away.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Don't wait for things to get better. Life will always be complicated. Learn to be happy right now. Otherwise, you'll run out of time.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 08, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'Healing isn't about changing who you are. It's about changing how you'feel you feel about who you are.'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'LOVE IS... When just being together is enough. Lo.'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 08, 2021. May be art of text.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 07, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'SAY GOODBYE TO THE PAST Because it's time to move on. It's time to be happy. Amazing things are on their th way.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 06, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Reminder: It's not your responsibility to correct somebody else's misunderstanding of you. -@FAIRYSFORUM'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 06, 2021. May be an image of sky and text that says 'Better days are coming. You have been through a lot. Now it' s time for you to shine.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 05, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Everything heals. Your body heals. Your heart heals. The mind heals. Wounds heal. Your soul repairs itself. Your happiness is always going to come back. Bad times don't last.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'One smile, can start a friendship. One word, can end a fight. One look, can save a relationship. One person can chänge your life.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 04, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'A huge shoutout to the people who haven't felt okay lately but still get up every day and refuse to quit, you got this. Unknown'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'When someone is broken, don't try to fix them. You can't). When someone is hurting, don't attempt to take away their pain. (You can't). Instead, love them by walking beside them in the hurt. (You can Because sometimes what people need is simply to know they aren't alone.'.
